        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tVuscUhwravlEUfbvu1M-97" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=13;spacing=10;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#CCCCCC;rounded=1;" value="&lt;b&gt;Data Flow&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;margin:4px 0&quot;&gt;1. User authenticates via Cognito&lt;br&gt;2. Uploads .docx via presigned URL to S3&lt;br&gt;3. S3 event notification triggers SQS message&lt;br&gt;4. ECS Worker polls SQS, downloads file&lt;br&gt;5. Worker calls Bedrock (Claude Sonnet 4.6)&lt;br&gt;   for multi-pass medical transcript annotation&lt;br&gt;6. Annotations saved to Results Bucket (JSON)&lt;br&gt;7. Job status updated in DynamoDB&lt;br&gt;8. User downloads results via presigned URL" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="260" width="380" x="2550" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tVuscUhwravlEUfbvu1M-98" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=12;spacing=8;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#CCCCCC;rounded=1;" value="&lt;b&gt;Legend&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;margin:4px 0&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash; Solid: Primary data flow&lt;br&gt;- - - - Dashed: Async / monitoring&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;- - - - Red dashed: Error path&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="110" width="260" x="2550" y="500" as="geometry" />
